### Get all screens
POST {{baseUrl}}/screens
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "token": "{{authToken}}"
}

### Create a new screen
POST {{baseUrl}}/screens/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "token": "{{authToken}}",
    "name": "Test Screen",
    "content": "Initial content for Test Screen"
}

### Get a specific screen
POST {{baseUrl}}/screens/get
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "token": "{{authToken}}",
    "screen_id": 1
}

